KeysToEntries.story_1_1_000:
Oh?
Didn’t expect to see you
back here.
KeysToEntries.story_1_1_001:
Didn’t think you’d actually
come all the way
to our turf…
KeysToEntries.story_1_1_002:
Heh…
I’ll admit it,
you’ve got guts.
KeysToEntries.story_1_1_003:
Coming to my turf
and asking me first?
Pretty harsh.
KeysToEntries.story_1_1_004:
I’ll stay in back—
show me what you got
against them.
KeysToEntries.story_1_1_005:
If you manage to win…
I’ll unleash
my true power.
